data.name: Acro Bike
rules: You may play as many Item cards as you like during your turn (before your attack).

data.name: Nest Ball
rules: You may play as many Item cards as you like during your turn (before your attack).
Search your deck for a Basic Pokémon and put it onto your Bench. Then, shuffle your deck.

data.name: Ultra Ball
rules: You may play as many Item cards as you like during your turn (before your attack).
Discard 2 cards from your hand. If you do, search your deck for a Pokémon, reveal it, and put it into your hand. Then, shuffle your deck.

data.name: Switch
rules: You may play as many Item cards as you like during your turn (before your attack).
Switch your Active Pokémon with 1 of your Benched Pokémon.

data.name: Pokémon Catcher
rules: You may play as many Item cards as you like during your turn (before your attack).
"Flip a coin. If heads, switch 1 of your opponents Benched Pokémon with their Active Pokémon."

data.name: Misty's Water Command
rules: You may play only 1 Supporter card during your turn (before your attack).
Move any number of Water Energy from your Pokémon to your Psyduck, Horsea, Staryu, Starmie-GX, Magikarp, Gyarados, or Lapras in any way you like.

data.name: Misty's Determination
rules: You may play only 1 Supporter card during your turn (before your attack).
Discard a card from your hand. If you do, look at the top 8 cards of your deck and put 1 of them into your hand. Shuffle the other cards back into your deck.
